{"tid":2113222,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打訓覺好撚易頸痛？","createTime":"2020-07-18T03:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T10:34:20.000Z","uid":299259,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0e6b04a4cd90e711a2edd94b7a2d14d6a3382d4e","tid":2113222,"uid":299259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T03:28:41.000Z","msg":"高又試過 低又試過<br />\n都係訓得唔舒服 訓醒條頸又酸又痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實係咪頸椎出左事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我上網睇話用啲cheapcheap cushion當枕頭反而會好啲<br />\n有無巴打有類似經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae894b4bdc5f88e08611d1d4f572b9440d66ff72","tid":2113222,"uid":149323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T03:35:25.000Z","msg":"玩得手機太多"},{"pid":"419dc7f502c8ba9b77df8b6e41189590326a61a1","tid":2113222,"uid":299259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae894b4bdc5f88e08611d1d4f572b9440d66ff72","tid":2113222,"uid":149323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T03:35:25.000Z","msg":"玩得手機太多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T03:38:56.000Z","msg":"應該唔關事 其實已經痛左好多年<br />\n有時訓醒無咁痛 有時痛到仆街<br />\n飲完酒訓醒又好似舒服啲<br />\n所以一直都無理<br />\n<br />\n其實係咪應該睇醫生<br />\n貴唔貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd26e9b92b7267d67a7e4b56697573ead574ea9a","tid":2113222,"uid":25520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T03:51:19.000Z","msg":"膊頭有冇痛？"},{"pid":"bd9c4def23002c9ad857c5282e407c27bde256f1","tid":2113222,"uid":299259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd26e9b92b7267d67a7e4b56697573ead574ea9a","tid":2113222,"uid":25520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T03:51:19.000Z","msg":"膊頭有冇痛？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T03:57:35.000Z","msg":"膊頭少 後背近頸個位痛多啲<br />\n條頸左右擰無問題<br />\n左右擺（即係好似印度人say yes咁）會扯住扯住<br />\n向後仰會痛<br />\n耷低頭反而唔痛"},{"pid":"7bac5169a3c9e2805cae281c9bf657c01d3b40d2","tid":2113222,"uid":102938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T03:58:36.000Z","msg":"以前瞓低枕頭就會頸痛<br />\n轉咗高枕頭之後就好少"},{"pid":"94814489a285ee45055fb567f2dd549e250665d5","tid":2113222,"uid":182180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:05:25.000Z","msg":"可能頸椎骨咩左，你試下搵Chiropractor 扭番正d骨，我都扭左幾個月先唔再痛"},{"pid":"ea6b342c257e65eba2df920542ab020d6d3aa15b","tid":2113222,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:06:13.000Z","msg":"同問留名"},{"pid":"bef54f0b0f35eb45257f570863dda61cf061da41","tid":2113222,"uid":29326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:08:34.000Z","msg":"唔用枕頭訓幾日好似好番少少 不過成晚會係咁郁<br />\n成日都訓唔好 跟住又更痛好鬼辛苦"},{"pid":"a94de7e587c4aa0e51c0863c0b1b0f71d130351a","tid":2113222,"uid":258847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:13:37.000Z","msg":"我瞓到個後腦都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該關枕頭事 試下買個軟啲嘅枕頭"},{"pid":"d1d785fc2ca314fa53d3d41e55e9512b135a8295","tid":2113222,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:14:40.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係床褥問題"},{"pid":"a7e7b90dd68905a4388aaa5d36c601afcd8fd1a9","tid":2113222,"uid":299259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1d785fc2ca314fa53d3d41e55e9512b135a8295","tid":2113222,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:14:40.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係床褥問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:28:43.000Z","msg":"由椰棕到彈簧再到加床墊都試過<br />\n都係痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4109e4affc49e4939d5d181f494937a86ddc218d","tid":2113222,"uid":299259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94814489a285ee45055fb567f2dd549e250665d5","tid":2113222,"uid":182180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":