ormal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be8acdad2e6a22234457668e0914e3d47f187094","tid":2113222,"uid":358731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:24:02.000Z","msg":"我都長期有呢個問題 換枕頭高高低低都冇用<br />\n痛到頸頭膊都郁唔到 直程落唔到床好誇張 個個月都會痛一鑊<br />\n睇專科脊醫都冇咩用 佢都係好溫柔咁幫我按下然後就叫我出去攤上床俾姑娘電吓 冇咩感覺<br />\n<br />\n後來我定期去針灸同走罐 即時都會舒服啲<br />\n去咗幾個月 宜家少咗出現痛楚 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好感動"},{"pid":"1a1bc0724dc6c7f8c2508af03f34216088e30405","tid":2113222,"uid":182180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4109e4affc49e4939d5d181f494937a86ddc218d","tid":2113222,"uid":299259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94814489a285ee45055fb567f2dd549e250665d5","tid":2113222,"uid":182180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:05:25.000Z","msg":"可能頸椎骨咩左，你試下搵Chiropractor 扭番正d骨，我都扭左幾個月先唔再痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:29:10.000Z","msg":"巴打有無好推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:35:12.000Z","msg":"我外國睇㗎，所以推介唔到俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但你揾個chiropractor 呢，一定要幫你照頸同脊骨 X-ray ，咁先睇到邊節骨咩左再去扭番正㗎。<br />\n<br />\n另外你可以試下呢種電子針炙筆，對付肌肉神經痛效果一流！佢有內置sensor 幫你揾 pressure points, 揾到會響嚟提示你㩒放電個button。通常pressure points 就係人痛嘅位置，而喺越痛d位置呢， 佢顯示個號碼就越大，個警鐘又會越響得大聲嚟提你好㩒放電個button啦。我痛到爆嘅位置，佢都找到好準確㗎，而電炙都有幾個levels俾你自己選擇。我自己用緊呢款<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkojFUi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkojFUi.jpg&h=27d167a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64a2bf64cbe63c9cfd9b81cee6094afae9f5636c","tid":2113222,"uid":299259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a1bc0724dc6c7f8c2508af03f34216088e30405","tid":2113222,"uid":182180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4109e4affc49e4939d5d181f494937a86ddc218d","tid":2113